{"id":417296,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/11/【图说天朝】没有国我们就什么都没有/","date":"2015-11-09T09:06:59Z","modified":"2015-11-09T09:06:59Z","title":"【图说天朝】没有国我们就什么都没有","content":"<p>@euphoriaMe：真是太恶心了，央逼一台在播啥鸡巴最美孝心少年，几个7，8岁的小孩每天吃一顿，天天走十几趟山路，剥玉米，采烟叶，两年存了1500块。拉到台中间一展览，肥得流油的董姓儿童节目主持人一下冲上台揽住小朋友的肩“你要爱家！更要爱国啊！有国才有家！没有国我们就什么都没有！”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/99LDD.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-417297\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/99LDD.jpg\" alt=\"99LDD\" width=\"600\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/99LDD.jpg 619w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/99LDD-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627],"tags":[8635,9540,10435,9465,29207]}